{
  "stem": "3341.1",
  "chunk_idx": 15,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was on the-- on a standard of a technical college of a-- like university with the title of engineer and so on.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was ready because I was starting to do all right, and I was proud what I was doing.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was sure that I will be there till I finish my study of four years.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But didn't happen because the political changes came.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "When-- when Hitler occupied Bohemia and Moravia militaristically, so they-- they considered me as a Slovakian citizen, coming from Slovakia.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That was a different country.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "German army didn't occupy Slovakia.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We became independent.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they declared one day in the school, every foreign nationals must go home.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was-- maybe that was lucky because that saved my life in the long run.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I was forced to go home to Slovakia, and there I was.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the anti-Jewish paragraphs, the Nuremberg laws, they were introduced immediately in Bohemia and Moravia very strictly.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "All Czech Jews were already sent to-- to concentration camps in Theresienstadt.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That was the first one.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We in Slovakia were terribly surprised and scared because we knew then we have-- we will have to follow.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then the Germans will not leave Slovakia as a independent state in the pocket, freedom to Jews, which unfortunately occurred, but not immediately.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Up to the year '41, the anti-Jewish laws were introduced slowly.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I had to go home.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To Bratislava.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My parents had very big business, my father.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So and-- I didn't-- I couldn't study.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There were no textile academy in Slovakia at all.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I was just helping in the firm of my-- my father, which was a-- we had retail shops, and we had wholesale business.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we had a lot of people, about 27 people, employed in the several shops.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
